ings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/undo_3_1.svg","title":"30-day risk-free return","ltitle":"","text":"","liquid":"","author":"","t-sec":false,"ratings":false,"v-buyer":false,"plink_label":"","plink":"","link_label":"","link":""}}},"block_order":["column_DiXRTH","column_DN6hqP","column_7tNzHR","column_DzAtqf","column_PMNP7P","column_wYWGG6"],"name":"t:sections.multicolumn.presets.name","settings":{"section-class":"logo-set","title":"","heading_size":"h1","image_width":"full","image_ratio":"adapt","button_label":"","button_link":"","columns_desktop":6,"column_alignment":"left","background_style":"primary","color_scheme":"scheme-6f2eec95-4ab6-4fd2-bec7-493789dbb910","columns_mobile":"2","swipe_on_mobile":false,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"mpadding_top":0,"mpadding_bottom":0}},"reviews_section_AdbtpG":{"type":"reviews-section","blocks":{"review_d36eCp":{"type":"review","settings":{"ntext":"<p>Stemba began because I couldn't find the place I needed. Juggling a full-time career, raising two daughters, and navigating serious health challenges of my own, I kept hitting the same wall: confusing information, unreliable tools, and a healthcare world that too often overlooked women. <br\/><br\/>Women deserve better than that.<br\/><br\/>The name comes from my daughters — Stella and Amber. Stemba is the company I want to exist for them. <br\/><br\/>We want to redefine women's wellness.<br\/><br\/><strong>And build something our daughters can one day rely on.<\/strong><br\/><br\/><\/p>","text":"","quote":false,"author":"","verified_label":""}},"review_xy6qfh":{"type":"review","settings":{"ntext":"<p><strong>Victoria Harverson<\/strong><br\/>Founder<\/p>","text":"","author_img":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/stemba-founder-victoria-hughes.jpg","quote":false,"author":"","verified_label":""}},"review_nPAw7a":{"type":"review","settings":{"ntext":"<p>Most women I work with in clinical practice are trying hard to manage their cycles, fertility, and pregnancies on information they have pieced together from apps, forums, and advice from family or friends. It is not their fault — women’s health has been under-studied, under-funded, and under-explained for too long.<br\/><br\/>They deserve tools built by professionals with genuine clinical expertise and experience, explained in language that respects their intelligence and is grounded in evidence.<br\/><br\/>That is why I came to Stemba. That is the work I am here to do.<br\/><br\/><br\/><\/p>","text":"","quote":true,"author":"","verified_label":""}},"review_LrkmQz":{"type":"review","settings":{"ntext":"<p><strong>Dr Katherine Clark<\/strong><br\/>Clinical Specialist, Stemba<br\/><br\/>PhD, Women's Health — King's College London<br\/>MSc Clinical Research, Distinction — King's College London<br\/>MSc Advanced Practice Midwifery, Distinction — King's College London<br\/>BSc Midwifery, First Class — Kingston University & St George's, University of London<\/p><p>Clinical Research Excellence Fellow — King's Health Partners, King's College London<br\/>Global PrAKI Consortium & Academy Lead<br\/>Published in The Lancet, Nature Reviews Nephrology, and Nephrology Dialysis Transplantation<\/p><p>Research partnerships with KKH and NUHS, Singapore<\/p>","text":"","author_img":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/stemba-clinical-specialist-dr-katherine-clark.jpg","quote":false,"author":"","verified_label":""}}},"block_order":["review_d36eCp","review_xy6qfh","review_nPAw7a","review_LrkmQz"],"name":"Reviews","settings":{"template":"template-2","pre_title":"Why Stemba exists","title":"From women, to women","show_underline":true}},"rich_text_fPXBQU":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"image_BqtFKw":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Vector_3.svg","img-class":"","b_radius":10,"heart-icon":false,"img-width":"","img-height":"","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":100,"mopadding_top":0,"mopadding_bottom":0}},"heading_3zgiEk":{"type":"heading","settings":{"t-class":"","heading":"Why Stemba exists","heading_size":"h1","hpadding_top":0,"hpadding_bottom":80,"mhpadding_top":60,"mhpadding_bottom":40}},"image_9T8pbf":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/stemba-founder-why-we-exist-mother-baby.jpg","img-class":"","b_radius":20,"heart-icon":false,"img-width":"714","img-height":"741","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":70,"mopadding_top":0,"mopadding_bottom":10}},"liquid_NWnPQy":{"type":"liquid","settings":{"liquid":"<div class=\"founder-statement-long\">\n  <p>\n    In today's world, women face a myriad of challenges when it comes to understanding their health, particularly around their cycles and fertility. For far too long, misinformation and unreliable tools have left many frustrated and confused. It became all too clear to me as I juggled my full-time job in fintech, raising two daughters, and grappling with my own health struggles — including strokes and other health challenges — that we deserve better.\n  <\/p>\n\n  <p>\n    Women spend a quarter of their lives in poor health, often overlooked in the healthcare ecosystem. It ignited a fire in me to pave a new path for women seeking accurate cycle and fertility tracking.\n  <\/p>\n\n  <p>\n    Thus, Stemba was born in 2023 with a singular goal: to empower women with precise and reliable solutions. As a working mother, I understand the overwhelming nature of navigating inaccurate fertility information — we are done with the noise.\n  <\/p>\n\n  <p>\n    Alongside my husband and a stellar team that includes Dr. Katherine, a clinical health expert, we brought Daysy to Stemba: a medical-grade cycle and fertility tracker with a 99.4% accuracy rate based on over 107,000 cycles tracked. This tool adapts to individual needs and learns your unique patterns without the noise of average-based data.\n  <\/p>\n\n  <p>\n    Imagine waking up every morning, effortlessly taking your temperature, and knowing within moments that you're equipped with information to better understand your reproductive health.\n  <\/p>\n\n  <p>\n    This isn't just about selling a product — it's about building a community that values women's health and wellness, and providing a trusted space where women feel understood, supported, and empowered.\n  <\/p>\n\n  <p class=\"founder-statement-closing\">\n    — Victoria, Founder\n  <\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n<style>\n  .founder-statement-long {\n    max-width: 720px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    text-align: center;\n    color: inherit;\n  }\n\n  .founder-statement-long p {\n    font-size: 16px;\n    line-height: 1.6;\n    font-weight: 400;\n    font-style: normal;\n    margin: 0 0 22px;\n  }\n\n  .founder-statement-long p:first-child {\n    font-style: italic;\n  }\n\n  .founder-statement-closing {\n    font-size: 15px !important;\n    margin-top: 28px !important;\n  }\n\n  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {\n    .founder-statement-long {\n      max-width: 100%;\n      text-align: left;\n    }\n\n    .founder-statement-long p {\n      font-size: 15px;\n      line-height: 1.55;\n      margin-bottom: 20px;\n    }\n  }\n<\/style>"}},"image_gpkTqw":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Vector_3.svg","img-class":"","b_radius":10,"heart-icon":false,"img-width":"","img-height":"","padding_top":100,"padding_bottom":10,"mopadding_top":60,"mopadding_bottom":0}}},"block_order":["image_BqtFKw","heading_3zgiEk","image_9T8pbf","liquid_NWnPQy","image_gpkTqw"],"name":"t:sections.rich-text.presets.name","settings":{"hr_enable":false,"a-sl":true,"section-class":"b-bottom h2-text","desktop_content_position":"center","content_alignment":"center","color_scheme":"scheme-2","full_width":true,"padding_top":150,"padding_bottom":150,"mopadding_top":68,"mopadding_bottom":90}},"rich_text_F44djB":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"bullet_point_K4TTzp":{"type":"bullet-point","settings":{"b-text":"Where to start"}},"heading_WMqxrL":{"type":"heading","settings":{"t-class":"","heading":"You don't have to","heading_size":"h1","hpadding_top":70,"hpadding_bottom":0,"mhpaddin